#

Ambrosia Apple Smoothie

5 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

SmoothieHealthyQuickBreakfast

Description

A refreshing and creamy smoothie bursting with the flavors of sweet apples and a hint of cinnamon, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • ambrosia apples: 2, cored and chopped
  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • almond milk (or any milk of choice): 1 cup
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
  • ice cubes: 1 cup
